Enum SortOrder

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SortOrder>

    public enum SortOrder
extends Enum<SortOrder>
    Defines in what order to perform sort operations.
    Since:
    0.9.8
    Author:
    Luc Boudreau

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ASC
      Ascending sort order.
      BASC
      Sorts in ascending order, but does not maintain members of a same hierarchy together.
      BDESC
      Sorts in descending order, but does not maintain members of a same hierarchy together.
      DESC
      Descending sort order.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ASC

        public static final SortOrder ASC
        Ascending sort order. Members of the same hierarchy are still kept together.

      • DESC

        public static final SortOrder DESC
        Descending sort order. Members of the same hierarchy are still kept together.

      • BASC

        public static final SortOrder BASC
        Sorts in ascending order, but does not maintain members of a same hierarchy together. This is known as a "break hierarchy ascending sort".

      • BDESC

        public static final SortOrder BDESC
        Sorts in descending order, but does not maintain members of a same hierarchy together. This is known as a "break hierarchy descending sort".
